{"tid":491155,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日媒：美或於本月18日發動斬首金正恩行動","createTime":"2017-12-06T08:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T09:03:11.000Z","uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ce215f408ebc9c09f0c47534dfa91da68a06ca55","tid":491155,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:48:21.000Z","msg":"日媒：美或於本月18日發動斬首金正恩行動<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/bknint-20171206151402022-1206_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171206%2Fbknint-20171206151402022-1206_17011_001.html&d=RrWYVrTiYs3SVwhRt8KSZOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=40b264f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/bknint-20171206151402022-1206_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n北韓發射洲際彈道導彈後，美國與南韓便舉行大型軍事演習，出動多款隱形戰機，令朝鮮半島局勢再度緊張。日本《產經新聞》周一（4日）報道，美國總統特朗普認為北韓不接受和平解決問題，所以決定對北韓發動先發制人的攻擊，對金正恩採取斬首行動，時間更可能是本月18日的「新月之夜」前後。<br />\n<br />\n《產經新聞》引述日本記者加賀孝英指，特朗普決定對金正恩發動斬首行動的消息，令各國情報當局的人員相當緊張。加賀孝英又引述美軍情報消息人士，解釋為何美軍選擇於本月18日發起斬首行動。首先是可攻擊美國本土的火星14型洲際彈道導彈，預料於今年底前完成研發，所以美國已經時日無多。其次是北韓自10月中開始核彈頭量產化，而潛伏在日韓的間諜有異常活動。<br />\n<br />\n最後，加賀孝英稱北韓人民軍在國際制裁下，現時處於饑餓狀態。金正恩為防軍方叛變，或在父親金正日死忌本月17日、或其生日1月8日前後，在朝鮮半島東部海域或太平洋上空，進行核試等「暴走」的行為。不過，有關消息仍未得到美國或南韓官方的證實，但南韓軍方早前成立專門執行對朝斬首行動的特種部隊。"},{"pid":"73c2ba3fd33518e0499ef34ef887020af24524f2","tid":491155,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984ad95a33ea269e4352a3931451224b1ac8713d","tid":491155,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:49:58.000Z","msg":"繼續吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c4f5b328d79ea4bafc7429bfa18905c44c9a92","tid":491155,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ff56fe5f81937018152d41e48bb749b5c6c8ab","tid":491155,"uid":19388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:57:36.000Z","msg":"Twitter戰士"},{"pid":"d42dc244ab7f151debd2248af3eb2212d1098e0f","tid":491155,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/JCwHQPz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJCwHQPz.jpg&h=25a021ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DZzxRBY.jpg?1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDZzxRBY.jpg%3F1&h=62084cc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4d6aaae5f8dd21e078d7c75d47062581ee3e630","tid":491155,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T08:58:57.000Z","msg":"嚇到金正恩晚晚都訓唔著 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706dba281296f960e77788ab32dba59bdba0d6ac","tid":491155,"uid":36148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T09:03:11.000Z","msg":"=__=  問過佢個好朋友洛文未？"}]}